snippet.title: My Review - Aaron Fischer
snippet.description:
I am a full time voice actor and a person who LOVES movies and TV shows. I have been reviewing movies since I was in high school and have been doing reviews on Facebook for the last 10 years with the title My Review. Now, I am doing reviews on all things movies and TV shows and reviews on other things as well.

I am a DC comics, Star Wars and Indiana Jones fanatic. 

Look for reviews on so many things here from movies and tv shows to product reviews and everything in-between.
